com.cognos.CAM_AAA.authentication

Interface ISearchFilter

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ISearchFilterConditionalExpression, ISearchFilterFunctionCall, ISearchFilterRelationExpression

    public interface ISearchFilter
    Defines the interface to use for accessing the search filter contained in the search expression of an IBM Cognos query. A search filter can be one of the following types: ISearchFilterConditionalExpression, ISearchFilterFunctionCall or ISearchFilterRelationExpression.
    See Also:
    ISearchFilterConditionalExpression, ISearchFilterFunctionCall, ISearchFilterRelationExpression
